ug und gesichtslose Puppen, tragen immer Ziegenwollsocken, lila Kleider und impfen nicht gerne, ohne unangenehme Fragen zu stellen.\u2026", "language": null, "image": null, "pagetype": "article", "links": ["http://www.facebook.com/waldorfinspiration", "https://twitter.com/TheWaldorfBlog", "http://www.instagram.com/waldorfinspiration", "https://www.pinterest.de/WaldorfBientje/", "https://waldorfinspiration.com/de/home-2", "https://waldorfinspiration.com/de/category/waldorf-inspiration", "https://waldorfinspiration.com/de/category/anthroposophie-und-waldorfpaedagogik", "https://waldorfinspiration.com/de/category/jahreszeitenfesten", "https://waldorfinspiration.com/de/contact", "#pll_switcher", "https://waldorfinspiration.com/en/", "https://waldorfinspiration.com/es/", "https://waldorfinspiration.com/", "https://waldorfinspiration.com/de/", "https://waldorfinspiration.com/de/home-2", "https://waldorfinspiration.com/de/category/waldorf-inspiration", "https://waldorfinspiration.com/de/category/anthroposophie-und-waldorfpaedagogik", "https://waldorfinspiration.com/de/category/jahreszeitenfesten", "https://waldorfinspiration.com/de/contact", "#pll_switcher", "https://waldorfinspiration.com/en/", "https://waldorfinspiration.com/es/", "https://waldorfinspiration.com/", "https://waldorfinspiration.com/de/home-2", "https://waldorfinspiration.com/de/category/waldorf-inspiration", "https://waldorfinspiration.com/de/category/anthroposophie-und-waldorfpaedagogik", "https://waldorfinspiration.com/de/category/jahreszeitenfesten", "https://waldorfinspiration.com/de/contact", "#pll_switcher", "https://waldorfinspiration.com/en/", "https://waldorfinspiration.com/es/", "https://waldorfinspiration.com/", "https://waldorfinspiration.com/de/home-2", "https://waldorfinspiration.com/de/category/anthroposophie-und-waldorfpaedagogik", "https://waldorfinspiration.com/de/das-bin-ich-eveline-clignett", "http://waldorfinspiration.com/de/contact", "https://www.facebook.com/waldorfinspiration", "htt